This section provides comprehensive insights into quarantine operations, including release patterns, detection methods, and threat categorization. It helps security teams understand what types of threats are being quarantined and monitor quarantine release activity to identify potential false positives or security policy effectiveness."},"name":"text - 0"},{"type":1,"content":{"json":"### Quarantine Release Trend<br>

**This visual displays the daily trend of emails released from quarantine by administrators. Monitoring this metric helps identify patterns in quarantine management and potential areas where policy adjustments may be needed to reduce unnecessary quarantines.**"},"name":"text - 1"},{"type":3,"content":{"version":"KqlItem/1.0","query":"//This query visualises the daily ammount of emails released from quarantine
