**These visuals display the daily trend of email-related security incidents, as well as the proportion of email incidents compared to the total number of incidents in Defender.**"},"name":"text - 6"},{"type":3,"content":{"version":"KqlItem/1.0","query":"// Filter for incidents that have at least one Email Security alert
